Package org.gvsig.educa.portableview.swing.editor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PortableViewAddLayerComponent
    Component which allows to user to select a layer to add into a PortableViewCompilation
    PortableViewCompilationEditor
    Interface of swing component which allow modify compilation
    PortableViewCompilationEditorListener
    Interface for listener of a PortableViewCompilationEditor which will be notified of wizard finalization
    PortableViewLayerPropertiesEditor
    Component which allow to user to modify properties of a FLayer
    PortableViewLayersEditor
    Component which shows all layers of a PortableViewCompilation and allows user to change it.
